<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="blackICT Sales Agent Commission Agreement">
    <title>Commission Agreement</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicons/ict.jpg">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"

      rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css"

      rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
    /* Disable printing */
    @media print { body { display: none !important; } }
    /* Watermark to deter screenshots */
    body::before {
      content: "Black ICT solutions limited";
      position: fixed;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
    }
    /* Disable text selection and copying */
    html, body, * {
      -webkit-user-select: none;
      -moz-user-select: none;
      -ms-user-select: none;
      user-select: none;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body oncontextmenu="return false;" onkeydown="(event.ctrlKey &amp;&amp; (event.key==='p' || event.key==='s')) &amp;&amp; event.preventDefault(); (event.keyCode===44) &amp;&amp; event.preventDefault();">
    <div class="container py-5">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Black ICT solutions Limited<br>
        <small class="text-muted">Commission Agreement for Airtel
          Enterprise-Product Commission Sales Agents</small></h1>
      <div class="accordion" id="agreementAccordion">
        <!-- Definitions -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne"> <button class="accordion-button"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne"

              aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne"> <i class="bi bi-card-text me-2"></i>1.
              Definitions </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>These definitions apply throughout this Agreement unless the
                context requires otherwise:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>"Airtel"</strong> means Airtel Uganda Limited.</li>
                <li><strong>"Products"</strong> means the suite of Airtel
                  Enterprise solutions set forth in Section 3.</li>
                <li><strong>"Qualified Sale"</strong> means a sale of a Product
                  to a Customer that is accepted and paid for by Airtel within
                  the Sales Window and reconciled by the Company.</li>
                <li><strong>"Sales Window"</strong> means the period from the
                  1st to the 26th day of each calendar month.</li>
                <li><strong>"Commission Period"</strong> means the calendar
                  month in which Qualified Sales occur.</li>
                <li><strong>"MRR/ARR"</strong> means Monthly or Annual Recurring
                  Revenue associated with Product subscriptions, as applicable.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Appointment & Scope -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo"> <i class="bi bi-briefcase me-2"></i>2.
              Appointment &amp; Scope </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ol>
                <li>The Company (Black ICT solutions) appoints the Agent
                  non-exclusively to promote, solicit, and close sales within
                  Uganda across Business, Institutional/Non-profit, and
                  Residential segments.</li>
                <li>The Agent shall not represent any competing products without
                  prior written consent from the Company.</li>
                <li><strong>Agent Credentials &amp; Portal Access:</strong>
                  Company issues a unique ID and portal account; Agent must
                  safeguard credentials.</li>
                <li><strong>Onboarding Documentation:</strong> Submit full legal
                  name, two valid phone numbers, National ID copy, bank/Airtel
                  Money account, LC1 letter, two references, academic
                  certificates.</li>
                <li><strong>Independent Contractor Status:</strong> No
                  employer-employee relationship; Agent handles all tax, NSSF,
                  PAYE, and benefits.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Products -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree"> <i class="bi bi-box-seam me-2"></i>3.
              Products </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Xstream Shared &amp; Dedicated Internet</strong>
                  (Fiber &amp; Wireless Microwave)</li>
                <li><strong>Leased Lines</strong>: Dedicated, private internet
                  connections providing guaranteed speeds and reliability for
                  businesses, unlike shared standard internet services.</li>
                <li><strong>Toll-Free Numbers</strong>: Callers reach the
                  business at no cost; business covers all call charges.</li>
                <li><strong>Bulk SMS</strong> (min. UGX 5M deposit)</li>
                <li><strong>Bulk Airtime</strong> (Prepaid Voice, min. UGX 5M
                  deposit)</li>
                <li><strong>Sponsored Data</strong>: Third party covers data
                  usage away from user plan.</li>
                <li><strong>Private APN</strong>: Secure, dedicated cellular
                  network separate from public internet.</li>
                <li><strong>Internet Smart Plans</strong> (min. 10 concurrent
                  users)</li>
                <li><strong>CUG (Closed User Group)</strong>: Restricted network
                  for designated members.</li>
                <li><strong>NaaS</strong>: Virtual network services delivered
                  via cloud subscription.</li>
                <li><strong>SIP Trunking</strong>: IP-based voice trunking over
                  IP-PBX.</li>
                <li><strong>Postpaid Voice</strong> (min. UGX 1M deposit)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Agent Obligations -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour"> <i class="bi bi-list-check me-2"></i>4.
              Agent Obligations </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ol>
                <li>Achieve a minimum of five (8) Qualified Sales per Commission
                  Period. Failure to exceed eight in the subsequent period
                  authorizes termination.</li>
                <li>Generate leads, conduct client meetings, prepare proposals,
                  and close deals at the Agent’s cost.</li>
                <li>Complete Company’s product, compliance, and CRM
                  certification before engaging customers.</li>
                <li>Adhere to Code of Conduct: no unauthorized discounts,
                  maintain branding standards, and protect customer data privacy
                  per PDPA/GDPR.</li>
                <li>Log all leads, prospects, and Qualified Sales in the portal
                  by the 26th, with supporting documentation.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Commission & Incentives -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive"> <i class="bi bi-currency-exchange me-2"></i>5.
              Commission &amp; Incentives </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Commission rates on total sales value per Commission Period:</p>
              <table class="table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Sales/Month</th>
                    <th>Rate</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td>1–19</td>
                    <td>15%</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>20+</td>
                    <td>18%</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
              <p> <strong>AGENT:</strong> Agent get 200k upon 70% of the
                target.<br>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Payment Terms -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix"> <i class="bi bi-wallet2 me-2"></i>6.
              Payment Terms </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ul>
                <li>Only sales reconciled by Airtel within the Sales Window
                  qualify.</li>
                <li>Commissions are calculated after reconciliation and paid on
                  the 10th of the following month in UGX.</li>
                <li>The Company reserves the right to withhold, set off, or
                  adjust commissions at its sole discretion for any disputed,
                  unverified, or non-compliant sale; its determination is final.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Support -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSeven"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven"> <i class="bi bi-life-preserver me-2"></i>7.
              Support </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>The Company and Airtel Uganda Limited will provide product
                training, branded marketing collateral, pricing guidelines, and
                post-sale technical support at no cost to the Agent.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Term, Amendment & Termination -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingEight"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseEight"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEight"> <i class="bi bi-x-circle me-2"></i>8.
              Term, Amendment &amp; Termination </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseEight" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ol>
                <li>This Agreement is effective on signature and continues until
                  either party terminates with 30 days’ written notice.</li>
                <li>The Company may amend these terms at any time, effective
                  immediately upon notice via portal or email; continued
                  performance signifies acceptance.</li>
                <li>Immediate termination for misconduct; breach of
                  confidentiality/compliance; two consecutive underperforming
                  periods; failure to exceed five sales following a five-sale
                  period.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Confidentiality & Miscellaneous -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingNine"> <button class="accordion-button collapsed"

              type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNine"

              aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNine"> <i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-2"></i>9.
              Confidentiality &amp; Miscellaneous </button> </h2>
          <div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#agreementAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Agent shall maintain confidentiality of all proprietary
                information. Intellectual property remains with its owner. Agent
                indemnifies the Company and Airtel Uganda Limited against losses
                from Agent’s actions. Liability is capped at the total
                commissions paid to Agent in the prior six months. This
                Agreement is governed by the laws of Uganda, with disputes
                resolved via arbitration in Kampala. This document constitutes
                the entire agreement between parties.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="js/js-bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
